---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Send Money to Trinidad - The Ultimate Guide">
	<main>
		<header class="hero">
			<h1>SEND MONEY HOME<br><span>AT STREET RATES</span></h1>
		</header>

		<div class="content">
			<section class="guide-section">
				<h2>‚≠êÔ∏è For Senders: Getting Started with Strike</h2>
				
				<h3>Step 1: Download Strike</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Download <a href="https://strike.me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Strike</a> from the App Store (iOS) or Google Play Store (Android)</li>
					<li>Open the app and click "Sign Up"</li>
					<li>Enter your phone number and verify with the code sent to you</li>
					<li>Complete your profile with basic information</li>
				</ul>

				<h3>Step 2: Verify Your Account</h3>
				<p>You'll need to provide:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Government-issued photo ID (Driver's License or Passport)</li>
					<li>Proof of address (utility bill, bank statement, or lease agreement less than 3 months old)</li>
					<li>Social Security Number (for US residents)</li>
					<li>A clear photo of yourself (selfie)</li>
				</ul>
				<div class="note">
					<strong>Note:</strong> Verification usually takes 1-2 business days. Make sure your documents are:
					<ul>
						<li>Clear and readable</li>
						<li>Not expired</li>
						<li>Show your current address</li>
						<li>Match the information you provided</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<h3>Step 3: Add Money to Strike</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Link your bank account or debit card</li>
					<li>Tap "Add Money"</li>
					<li>Enter the amount you want to transfer</li>
					<li>Select your funding source</li>
					<li>Confirm the deposit</li>
				</ul>

				<h3>Step 4: Send Money</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Tap the "Pay" button</li>
					<li>Enter the recipient's Strike username or phone number</li>
					<li>Enter the amount you want to send</li>
					<li>Add a note (optional)</li>
					<li>Review and confirm the payment</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="guide-section">
				<h2>‚≠êÔ∏è For Recipients: Getting Your Cash</h2>
				
				<h3>Step 1: Set Up Strike</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Download Strike (same process as above)</li>
					<li>Create your account</li>
					<li>Verify your identity when prompted</li>
				</ul>

				<h3>Step 2: Receive the Money</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Once the sender completes their transfer, you'll get a notification</li>
					<li>Open Strike to see the payment</li>
					<li>The money is now in your Strike account</li>
				</ul>

				<h3>Step 3: Cash Out at Guap ATM</h3>
				<p>Location: M6 Plaza, Trinidad and Tobago</p>
				<p>To get your cash:</p>
				<ol>
					<li>Visit the Guap ATM at M6 Plaza</li>
					<li>Select "Cash Out"</li>
					<li>Enter the amount you want to withdraw</li>
					<li>Follow the on-screen instructions</li>
					<li>Collect your cash</li>
				</ol>
			</section>

			<section class="guide-section">
				<h2>üöÄ Important Tips</h2>
				
				<h3>For Senders</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Make sure you have enough funds in your linked account</li>
					<li>Double-check the recipient's Strike username before sending</li>
					<li>Keep your Strike app updated</li>
					<li>Send during Guap ATM operating hours for immediate cash pickup</li>
				</ul>

				<h3>For Recipients</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Make sure you have access to your phone for verification</li>
					<li>Check Guap's operating hours before visiting</li>
					<li>Have your Strike account fully verified before receiving money</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="guide-section">
				<h2>Why Use Guap?</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Get street rates (7.5)</li>
					<li>Zero transfer fees</li>
					<li>Instant transfers</li>
					<li>Safe and secure</li>
					<li>Convenient ATM location</li>
					<li>No need to visit traditional money transfer offices</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="guide-section">
				<h2>Need Help?</h2>
				<p>Having trouble? We're here to help:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>WhatsApp support: +1 (868) 349-0993</li>
					<li>Visit our ATM location at M6 Plaza</li>
					<li>Message us on social media</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="cta-text">Start saving money on your transfers today! üí∏</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		color: white;
		font-size: 18px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	.hero {
		background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/hero-bg.jpg') center/cover;
		padding: 8rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 4.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		line-height: 1.1;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}
	h1 span {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		display: block;
	}
	.content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem;
	}
	.guide-section {
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--accent));
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	h2 {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
		font-size: 2rem;
	}
	h3 {
		color: white;
		margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}
	ul, ol {
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.note {
		background: rgba(var(--accent), 0.1);
		border-left: 4px solid rgb(var(--accent));
		padding: 1rem;
		margin: 1rem 0;
	}
	.note ul {
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}
	a {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	.cta-text {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		h1 {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
		.hero {
			padding: 4rem 1rem;
		}
		.content {
			padding: 1rem;
		}
		h2 {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}
		h3 {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}
	}
</style>